</b></p><p>Sun, Oct 25, 2020, 5:29‚ÄØAM</p><p>to wendell@nesmith.net</p><p><br /></p><p>Hi Wendell.</p><p><b>Im a biiiiiiig fan of your yt channel. I started watching a few weeks ago and i love your videos. u might even call me a fangirl. I just wanted to say HI! Its soooo good to see someone who really understands the world and doesnt fall for the lies. What do you think.</b></p><p><br /></p><p>Wendy</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>Sun, Oct 25, 2020, 5:38‚ÄØAM</p><p>to wendy.Smith2008</p><p><br /></p><p>Hi Wendy,</p><p><br /></p><p>Thank you so much for your kind words. They really mean a lot to me. Your heart is so beautiful. I don't get a lot of positive feedback doing what I do. Everybody is so brainwashed and it is hard to get them to budge on anything. Your words of encouragement will help me write more positively in my book I am currently writing. Thank you.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>wendy.Smith2008 <wendy.Smith2008@protonmail.com></p><p>Sun, Oct 25, 2020, 9:22‚ÄØPM</p><p>to Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>i would love to hear what book are you currently working on? What is it about? I dont know why you get soooo much hate from other people. Some people dont understand you and others are just nasty. people at school are nasty to me too and my parents dont understand me so i think i know how you feel. Its like the system is designed to lift up bad people while putting down good people.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendy</p><p><br /></p><p>‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê Original Message ‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê</p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>Sun, Oct 25, 2020, 10:28‚ÄØPM</p><p>to wendy.Smith2008</p><p><br /></p><p>You are very wise to see these things Wendy. Society is definitely geared to lift up the bad people and put down the good - exactly as you said it. My book is, in a way, sinister. It is insulting the reader and every human in the world. But the book is declared as not written for 