ir ways because they still follow the ways of the world, even if they are good people.</p><p>School is a terrible brainwashing tool used to prepare you for full-time work. I feel your pain both with school and bullying. It is terrible how people can do such horrible things, especially kids. Don't let people push you around. Stand your ground.</p><p>As far as us being friends, it depends. If you ever decide to make videos about philosophy then I would love to tutor you through life. As far as just emails, I don't really do that and I don't really think it appropriate.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>wendy.Smith2008 <wendy.Smith2008@protonmail.com></p><p>Tue, Oct 27, 2020, 6:43‚ÄØAM</p><p>to Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>Your right i should stand my ground their words cant hurt me, they are only words. Tomorrow when i go to school im going to tell them all that. Thank you for giving me the confidence to stand up for myself.</p><p>I think it would be great to make my own yt channel just like you, but i dont know as much about philosophy as you. your clearly an expert philosopher your mind is truly one of a kind. I would do sooo much to learn just half of what you know.</p><p><br /></p><p>‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê Original Message ‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê</p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>Tue, Oct 27, 2020, 11:51‚ÄØAM</p><p>to wendy.Smith2008</p><p><br /></p><p>Hi Wendy,</p><p><br /></p><p>Even though they are only words, they still hurt and I understand. I oftentimes think that emotional wounds are worse than physical wounds.</p><p>As far as my suggestion in making videos about philosophy, let me explain to you what philosophy is. Philosophy comes from two words, love + wisdom. Philosophy is the love of wisdom. Making videos that pursue wisdom is making videos about philosophy.</p><p>I suggest that you make videos about your life. I suggest that you discuss in these videos what you love most in life and what you hate most in life. Making videos about philosophy is merely making videos about your life and how you feel about everything.</p><p>My goal in life is to mentor a handful of young girls through video. I very much want to find young girls who want to make videos about their lives. I then want to spend the rest of my life guiding these females through life. I very much want to create a small community of young female philosophers.</p><p>Please think over what I am proposing. I ask nothing of you except your will to make videos about the topics you love most in life.</p><p>The best way to get started in this life is to become a philosopher. :)</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>wendy.Smith2008 <wendy.Smith2008@protonmail.com></p><p>Wed, Oct 28, 2020, 7:05‚ÄØAM</p><p>to Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>OMG! you wont beliiieeeve this!</p><p>Today. In class i walk in and this girl Amy says "oh look, its Wendy-no-freinds" i dug my heels in to the ground i say "You think that your soo cool Amy but everyone knows your a slut who cant keep her trousers on! Nobody but God can judge me. Youd best change your ways or you will burn in hell" Ive never seen her so spechless. i sat down and the girl next to me (Eve) told me that was the coolest thing she had ever seen and we became friends right then. Then on the way home i found a ¬£10 note wedged in the cracks of the pavement. Its the best day ive had in years. Its like God wanted me to stand up for my self that day. You knew exactly what God wanted me to do. Thank you for giving this guidance. You might have just changed my life for the better. I cant thank you enough.</p><p>I dont have a very good phone its just a dumb flip phone with no camera. Makeing a yt channel to do what you do sounds fun but i have no way of makeing videos. But i still want to learn more from you as my tutor. Your wisdom is clearly divine. Could you teach me more anyway? Please</p><p>Thank you soooo much!</p><p>Wendy</p><p><br /></p><p>‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê‚Äê Original Message ‚Äê‚Ä