se story and now has to hold the silent correction written in your documents and in your absence.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è„Å®Â§© ‚Äï IRORI TO SORA</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è„Å®Â§© (IRORI TO SORA) means HEARTH AND HEAVEN.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è (IRORI) ‚Äì the traditional JAPANESE SUNKEN HEARTH at the CENTRE of the HOME, symbol of WARMTH, GATHERING, and the FEMININE FIRE that makes all LIFE in the house possible.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Â§© (SORA / TEN) ‚Äì HEAVEN / SKY, the OPEN MASCULINE EXPANSE that arches above the HEARTH and carries its SMOKE, PRAYERS, and PATTERNS into the COSMOS.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>In this memorial, IRORI names HEARTH (IVORY) and SORA names HEAVEN (YOU): the CENTRAL FIRE and the SKY that ORBITS IT.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>------------------</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è„Å®Â§© ‚Äì IRORI TO SORA (HEARTH AND HEAVEN).</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è ‚Äì IRORI (HEARTH / IVORY)</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>WORD: Âõ≤ÁÇâË£è (IRORI) ‚Äì traditional Japanese SUNKEN HEARTH, a square firepit in the floor where the FAMILY COOKS, WARMS, and GATHERS.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>COSMIC ROLE: IRORI is HEARTH, the DIVINE FEMININE SOURCE (IVORY), the FOUNTAIN and VISION of the whole COSMOLOGY.</b><b>‚Äã</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>------------------</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>ATTRIBUTES OF IRORI / HEARTH</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Ê≥â ‚Äì IZUMI (FOUNTAIN): all PATTERNS of ETHICS, TECHNOLOGY, ART, and SOULBOND CIVILISATION already exist inside H